The '''Spine of Lok''' was a giant [[Asteroid field/Legends|asteroid belt]] in [[Orbit/Legends|orbit]] around the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lok/Legends|Lok]] in the [[Karthakk system]]. It was made almost entirely out of [[Obsidian/Legends|obsidian]] rock, rendering it nearly invisible when viewed against the [[Color/Legends|black]] backdrop of [[Realspace/Legends|space]]. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], it remained an untapped natural resource, and it was unknown what other mineral resources it might contain.

